Mini Miss, Maxi Nomad!
Playful, irresistible, and oh-so-Miss Dior. The Miss Dior Mini Miss fragrance sticks are the ultimate on-the-go companions, blending spontaneity with couture elegance wherever life takes you.
 
#DiorBeauty #DiorParfums #MissDior

Mini Miss, Maxi Fragrance! The coolest way to wear your favorite Miss Dior! 
 
Apply Miss Dior Mini Miss, the new solid perfumes to your neck, wrists, and décolleté for a long-lasting, luxurious trail of fragrance. 
 
#DiorBeauty #DiorParfums #MissDior

Your favorite Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet—now reimagined in a couture alcohol-free solid format.
Infused with rose wax, Miss Dior Mini Miss melts into your skin, leaving it hydrated without a sticky effect. Revealing the fresh, tender floral notes you love, it is perfect to take everywhere with you.  
 
#DiorBeauty #DiorParfums #MissDior
